{"tid":1529478,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"我地真正要學習嘅國家其實係以色列","createTime":"2019-09-01T17:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T14:06:24.000Z","uid":267047,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7e925a3070629777e295702d14ae2e01d1a609d8","tid":1529478,"uid":267047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:50:38.000Z","msg":"以色列是一個真正實現了全民皆兵的國家。以色列憲法規定，年滿18歲的男女青年必須服兵役。男子服義務兵役年限為4年，而後轉入預備役，直至年滿41歲；女子服義務兵役為3年，而後轉入預備役，直至年滿34歲。預備役期間，每年有一個月戰備值勤，因此以色列人戲稱自己是「11個月不在位的士兵」。<br />\n<br />\n以色列常備軍的規模不大，但它的戰爭動員能力極強：它能夠在戰鬥發生後的18小時內，讓全體預備役軍人領取武器，完成集結；在36小時內，讓預備役部隊投入作戰。而且，以色列預備役部隊的作戰素質和承擔的作戰任務與現役部隊區別不大。<br />\n<br />\n長文在此：<a href=\"https://www-epochtimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org/v/www.epochtimes.com/b5/16/2/19/n4643287.htm/amp?amp_js_v=a2&amp;amp_gsa=1&amp;usqp=mq331AQEKAFwAQ%3D%3D#aoh=15673596125776&amp;referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com&amp;amp_tf=%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90%EF%BC%9A%251%24s&amp;ampshare=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F16%2F2%2F19%2Fn4643287.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-epochtimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fv%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F16%2F2%2F19%2Fn4643287.htm%2Famp%3Famp_js_v%3Da2%26amp_gsa%3D1%26usqp%3Dmq331AQEKAFwAQ%253D%253D%23aoh%3D15673596125776%26referrer%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.google.com%26amp_tf%3D%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%25BA%2590%25EF%25BC%259A%25251%2524s%26ampshare%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.epochtimes.com%252Fb5%252F16%252F2%252F19%252Fn4643287.htm&d=c1rUz8TxCzzDRK4zYpKqdM83aCWJNbCOh4I0%2FkJBrkU%3D&h=63aa68e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www-epochtimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org/v/www.epochtimes.com/b5/16/2/19/n4643287.htm/amp?amp_js_v=a2&amp;amp_gsa=1&amp;usqp=mq331AQEKAFwAQ%3D%3D#aoh=15673596125776&amp;referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com&amp;amp_tf=%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90%EF%BC%9A%251%24s&amp;ampshare=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F16%2F2%2F19%2Fn4643287.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5630fdcb44c3f89bd129e21b24c9fb47b019fd86","tid":1529478,"uid":5378,"like":11,"dislike